{"tid":2011723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急市民所急] 關愛基金撥4.5億　助8萬基層戶換數碼電視或機頂盒","createTime":"2020-05-11T07:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T08:54:39.000Z","uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddffed42ec6361f32d0efc613d799be641b446a","tid":2011723,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"關愛基金撥4.5億　助8萬基層戶換數碼電視或機頂盒<br />\n<br />\n政府已落實今年12月1日起終止模擬電視廣播，並全面進行數碼廣播。政府將推出援助計劃，為有需要援助的模擬電視住戶添置數碼電視接收器材，例如加裝機頂盒、更換數碼電視機等。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華稱，將透過關愛基金斥資4.5億元，料8萬個低收入、長者等合資格基層戶受惠。"},{"pid":"6cccc47ea92362f6bfe79ffb87b56dd6d7236a56","tid":2011723,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f0adeb3d6e73b78a3948bba878290f8bfe0233","tid":2011723,"uid":55321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"on9"}]}